OL,3,CShortage of pilots likely to impact
OL,4,CAurigny, report finds
OL,6,FExperts say Aurigny is likely to face
OL,7,Fchallenges in the future - as an
OL,8,Fongoing shortage of experienced pilots
OL,9,Fimpacts the airline.
OL,11,FThe comments are part of a new inquiry
OL,12,Fwhich was commissioned by Guernsey's
OL,13,FStates and undertaken by two experts
OL,14,Ffrom British Airways - former Chief
OL,15,FPilot Douglas Brown and ex-finance
OL,16,Fdirector of a BA subsidiary Mark
OL,17,FElliott.
OL,19,FThe pair concluded that much of the
OL,20,Fdisruption was beyond the airline's
OL,21,Fcontrol, but did raise some red flags.
