OL,3,CShortage of pilots likely to impact
OL,4,CAurigny, report finds
OL,6,F"Virtually every UK carrier is
OL,7,Fsuffering crew shortfalls" and Aurigny
OL,8,Fwill need to take "extraordinary
OL,9,Fmeasures to secure and retain
OL,10,Fqualified flight crew".
OL,12,FThey referenced the cost of housing as
OL,13,Fa problem which impacts staff
OL,14,Frecruitment and retention.
OL,16,FA common theme is the difficulty
OL,17,FAurigny has in operating around the
OL,18,Fopening times of the airline, and the
OL,19,Freport says a review into opening
OL,20,Ftimes is needed.
