OL,3,CShortage of pilots likely to impact
OL,4,CAurigny, report finds
OL,6,FAfter punctuality of its aircrafts
OL,7,Ffell from 75.1% in 2023 to 64.9% in
OL,8,F2024, the inquiry also said the year's
OL,9,Fsummer schedule had "potentially
OL,10,Fpushed the capacity of the fleet to
OL,11,Fits limit".
OL,13,FIt was confident, however, of a
OL,14,Frecovery in 2025: "The schedule that
OL,15,Fhas been put forward would appear to
OL,16,Fhave more resilience for winter 24-25
OL,17,Fand especially for the summer season
OL,18,Fof 2025".
