OL,3,CShortage of pilots likely to impact
OL,4,CAurigny, report finds
OL,6,FFurthermore, the review agreed with
OL,7,Fthe decision to sell the Embraer jet
OL,8,Fin November last year, saying: "if it
OL,9,Fhad been kept in the fleet the
OL,10,Fsituation might have been even worse
OL,11,Fthan what was experienced.
OL,13,FThe investigation revealed "certain
OL,14,Fsituations and practices that we found
OL,15,Funusual" and "the resilience of air
OL,16,Fservices on the island could be
OL,17,Fenhanced and with smoother and more
OL,18,Freliable operations".
