OL,3,CShortage of pilots likely to impact
OL,4,CAurigny, report finds
OL,6,FCEO of the States-owned airline, Nico
OL,7,FBezuidenhout, said: "We're making sure
OL,8,Fthat we have got the aircraft
OL,9,Favailable to service our schedule,
OL,10,Fthat the schedule is reasonable and
OL,11,Fachievable and that we've got pilots
OL,12,Fto fly those aircraft.
OL,14,F"These are the three main areas where
OL,15,Fwe are exerting effort".
